{"tid":89864,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實LS究竟點考高分？","createTime":"2017-01-21T15:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T13:16:24.000Z","uid":27097,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"59743e71d641be425880a6580aea1777e1612280","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"我真係好想好想知，LS其實點先可以考得高分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其paper 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> paper 1我都算幾好但paper 2真係......<br />\n請各位巴打多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e75453e0cdd5f55ea3083967bdad14dc9c0d48","tid":89864,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"寫靚d字"},{"pid":"5c9fbf4ae6b65b8bf14f045505c93dac6dde5828","tid":89864,"uid":63127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"記多D論據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   有結構性咁答題"},{"pid":"a86c135da19f18e9b14e783cbadb3e6f11b70d00","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記多D論據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   有結構性咁答題</blockquote><br />\n咁論點係咪配合返source(即係stakeholders嘅stance)會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n齋寫自己意見好似好高風險咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d66cfcad373d32eeb79926ddf40d1b98fd1c78","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫靚d字</blockquote><br />\n多謝你，不過我覺得自己係技巧上嘅不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf11145a01f04e62f4a1e8c52fe2c049c65a2983","tid":89864,"uid":454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0