rmal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 審題嗰陣睇清楚啲字眼 比佢trap到隨時IR扣哂啲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1056e60c84f9c1d211a86dbeae09eeb1efe7a2f","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗到咩就將佢變做書面語照寫 寫得愈多愈有著數</blockquote><br />\npaper 2佢淨係寫咗句how about other means?<br />\n之後嗰十幾廿行嘅argument咁就0咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有例子佢都好似睇唔明咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇返model answer冇依個argument<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一個喺source抄出嚟，但寫中model answer嘅argument反而full mark<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我更加肯定LS唔係睇你個人見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係抄source砌字砌例子嘅遊戲<br />\n亦都可能係我諗嘢太冇邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3a38fe942f4d08655810bd2d31d2a68454b6ad","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常寫下啲概念詞 例子 夠量就可以<br />\n個結構段段一樣咁濟<br />\n16DSE 5** 不過IES差唔多滿分<br />\n有興趣嘅可以問我拎份卷睇下<br />\n巴打加油啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打點溫LS？<br />\n依個問題好似好傻咁...<br />\npaper 2啲argument係咪可以喺source直抄？<br />\n求救呀巴打LS都真係溫唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsource係咪大曬㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fe6604ccb85e09e4a13da26c3f3543457c5e79","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用多啲概念詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 審題嗰陣睇清楚啲字眼 比佢trap到隨時IR扣哂啲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得我審題好唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e39a96824208473458e1eefeb37f0e7dd5d8e35","tid":89864,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"IES高分"},{"pid":"be966ef6331d86e21174d781281aa7a4e1c5cf40","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IES高分</blockquote><br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb2c62fffa72eba59c5899473a7633f4ca016b1","tid":89864,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>IES高分</blockquote><br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同老師打好關係 刷多啲鞋"},{"pid":"599d88519c48e4fd4b079efc9440db6c31a4e59c","tid":89864,"uid":2241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:46:31.000Z","msg":"平時睇多啲報紙 了解不同立場 <br />\n背下概念+審題 特別字眼要諗清楚 <br />\n要有topic sentence"},{"pid":"afa9be18b42c6916890f59ef946c04616399d049","tid":89864,"uid":47700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用多啲概念詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 審題嗰陣睇清楚啲字眼 比佢trap到隨時IR扣哂啲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得我審題好唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見你上面有問paper 2啲sources點處理<br />\n其實paper 2佢比嘅資料都會有啲point係度 佢會比到啲hints你答問題<br />\n你可以寫左自己個point先，再寫從資料顯示，xxxxxxxxxxxx   quote 返句野出黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但paper 2最好答多啲本身資料無嘅例子support你嘅point <br />\nPaper2嘅話仲有如果你諗到有啲point係同條問題有關但資料無都可以寫落去 唔好比資料guide住你諗野 局住自己只係可以睇資料啲hints黎諗point 要記住paper2嘅資料都係輔助性 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">不過我覺得Ls要高分最主要都係要練好嗰套答題框架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為point同例子來來去去都係嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"324144c1ff0f35b8d7415cf77c3cf5f7f1e9b9ec","tid":89864,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:01:27.000Z","msg":"靠運氣<br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人"},{"pid":"5c4909fc83c21b4e1056551b1ef6126924febbe1","tid":89864,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠運氣<br />\n利申 過來人</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n當年校內屈機 去到中六跌watt 心諗識用topic sentence識拆字識elaborate識點答中條題目 應該有5呱 點知考個日好緊張 Paper2答唔切 turnout 5都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1c9165e4b28b69d6d731a76656c8bd04fba6d4","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用多啲概念詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 審題嗰陣睇清楚啲字眼 比佢trap到隨時IR扣哂啲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得我審題好唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見你上面有問paper 2啲sources點處理<br />\n其實paper 2佢比嘅資料都會有啲point係度 佢會比到啲hints你答問題<br />\n你可以寫左自己個point先，再寫從資料顯示，xxxxxxxxxxxx   quote 返句野出黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但paper 2最好答多啲本身資料無嘅例子support你嘅point <br />\nPaper2嘅話仲有如果你諗到有啲point係同條問題有關但資料無都可以寫落去 唔好比資料guide住你諗野 局住自己只係可以睇資料啲hints黎諗point 要記住paper2嘅資料都係輔助性 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">不過我覺得Ls要高分最主要都係要練好嗰套答題框架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為point同例子來來去去都係嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以畀telegram我畀我再問問你關於LS嘅問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實我絲打嚟放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n其實LS係咪要操卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fa6d1e33a1f650f73877125acad0558368225b","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靠運氣<br />\n利申 過來人</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n當年校內屈機 去到中六跌watt 心諗識用topic sentence識拆字識elaborate識點答中條題目 應該有5呱 點知考個日好緊張 Paper2答唔切 turnout 5都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果巴打都咁樣嘅話我可能出到去都得個2/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e552f33617b60dbc8ec97c1ddd38916f409d7e8","tid":89864,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"823da852b01e1dbdeb76bca24f91c7473f0fc1c9","tid":89864,"uid":33163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常寫下啲概念詞 例子 夠量就可以<br />\n個結構段段一樣咁濟<br />\n16DSE 5** 不過IES差唔多滿分<br />\n有興趣嘅可以問我拎份卷睇下<br />\n巴打加油啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass