ets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想問考之前嗰晚係咪一定要早瞓同埋操卷有冇用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相信考咩都要早瞓 自己習慣<br />\n操卷我就冇真係寫落去<br />\n都係Miss上堂講個題型 點拆字<br />\n自己諗下個Point再對下Marking Scheme<br />\n我就覺得有啲Point係百搭嘅就記左佢算</blockquote><br />\n好呀唔該曬巴打，我會自己鑽研下啲marking scheme<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5d4e6cf028fb073d374e224e64a1bea732a1d4","tid":89864,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"睇新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6338a65f7f711456e06c145173e753f49ec3b20","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咁反共得咁反共<br />\nIes 8x/100<br />\n2014 LS 5*<br />\n校內第一次test10分定11分滿分拎得嗰3、4分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經好反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係上次exam paper 2我答嗰題係宣誓釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我激動得滯狂寫離曬題之後得8/20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2790dd41916d002566014cd9b2deb9a4f0df9653","tid":89864,"uid":42527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得ls呢樣野係鬥寫字快 推論完唔完整<br />\n講真個句 概念詞呢啲野我就覺得冇咩需要要背<br />\n當你睇啲報紙（信報通識etc)入面講嘅概念詞<br />\n你就知乜鳩都可以係概念詞 根本唔洗刻意去背 <br />\n寧願著眼係推論仲好 再用手速堆爆啲字數出黎就可以"},{"pid":"a9fa81b188a8842d93a83629070ac7b258c3d16e","tid":89864,"uid":454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買返份卷 paper2仲高過1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  校內就調轉</blockquote><br />\n巴打點做到<br />\n係咪study leave嗰陣做過啲咩嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好苦惱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係paper1失手 paper2類似嘅題自己做過幾次"},{"pid":"b05a7c9615cd7626b295a2c43a8d2afe4eb38137","tid":89864,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咁反共得咁反共<br />\nIes 8x/100<br />\n2014 LS 5*<br />\n校內第一次test10分定11分滿分拎得嗰3、4分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經好反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係上次exam paper 2我答嗰題係宣誓釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我激動得滯狂寫離曬題之後得8/20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年有位師兄教我<br />\n推論要做到畫公仔畫出腸<br />\n當正eaa班友係咩都唔識<br />\n<br />\n當你個推論好嚴密針都插唔入嗰陣<br />\n你唔使點用好多concept都可以好分<br />\n<br />\n仲有落筆前要睇下自己有咩point<br />\n越重嗰啲越放前<br />\n<br />\n同埋rebuttal唔好寫完就算<br />\n要簡單咁推論下講下點解個相反觀點好似成立"},{"pid":"04b2ae2d08da7cb4a0edf7a55047d2ee47c4db29","tid":89864,"uid":47700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以畀telegram我畀我再問問你關於LS嘅問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實我絲打嚟放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n其實LS係咪要操卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 可以 不過我telegram無set username<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如你比你username我 我add你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLs係要操卷 要練熟個答題框架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n@psyduckpsy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特登改咗，本來用真名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSend左野比你啦 唔知你收唔收到 因為我真係唔多識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33598814c303f98b39fff38643d3b89060e906f","tid":89864,"uid":46054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"每一個module 都有好多野可以預先背定先入去考嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係唔好走去背書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想快速進步的話讀熟marking (e.g evaluate suggestions, roles of government and NGO, personal growth 嘅概念, HK today 仲未出過嘅恆常議題) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  清晰topic sentence + 概念化 + 一兩個例子已經好夠做<br />\n<br />\n同埋考之前記住溫熟題型！邊D要比 stance要識分 (discuss 同evaluate 有時都要)，有時都會有D題目暗地裏需要你做comparison，如果係paper 2就最好唔好揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 2016 DSE LS 5**"},{"pid":"27665eefe9ad631e65c043d933e3af4a1654ef49","tid":89864,"uid":34205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:28:49.000Z","msg":"根本呢科就on99<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，校內試兩份夾埋3分，留名自救"},{"pid":"1d08d99b5b7be98aa7509f86053d2a06efa60676","tid":89864,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"答題有原則<br />\n立場來自原則<br />\n論點來自立場<br />\n論據唔好咁窄<br />\n展示下你世界視野<br />\n<br />\n但唔好用錯例子<br />\n<br />\n留意答題既因果關係"},{"pid":"db2e720dec52c64792ee8dea08653b2e9deea8a4","tid":89864,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答題有原則<br />\n立場來自原則<br />\n論點來自立場<br />\n論據唔好咁窄<br />\n展示下你世界視野<br />\n<br />\n但唔好用錯例子<br />\n<br />\n留意答題既因果關係</blockquote><br />\n利申：準備做通識教畜"},{"pid":"b931f39e45a68effe9aec3017b5d5e1ff36053e1","tid":89864,"uid":31523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"自己經驗覺得唔一定要份份卷操晒 但一定一定要熟唔同題型 記住係操題型唔係操問題<br />\n第二係推論一定要愈仔細愈好 總之當條友弱智乜都寫晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有概念詞記得就記啦 記唔到其實自己加啲乜乜化 乜乜性都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申16dse 5** 不過我ies 差唔多滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有咩問題幫到一定幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ffc9e1d11423f4c18e2687d6c9177caf0cc541","tid":89864,"uid":200266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"其實都有技巧嘅，就係要諗嘢清晰，有機會就入佢中路<br />\n利申:攞1"},{"pid":"ec31a10e5db7273a185134f5228dbc807c748b16","tid":89864,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49ffc9e1d11423f4c18e2687d6c9177caf0cc541","tid":89864,"uid":200266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"其實都有技巧嘅，就係要諗嘢清晰，有機會就入佢中路<br />\n利申:攞1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"寫句我條賓周長過長洲已經夠攞5**啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /